<D>__{have you done something to your hair?}
<A>__{ripley starts to smile, his eyes darting around the room.}
<C>__{ripley}
<D>__{freddie, do you have something to say?}
<C>__{freddie}
<D>__{what? i think i'm saying it. something's going on. he's either converted to christianity or to something else.}
<C>__{ripley}
