<C>__{freddie}
<D>__{is it on "delle croce, just off the corso" ? you're a quick study, aren't you? last time you didn't know your ass from your elbow, now you're giving me directions. that's not fair, you probably do know your ass from your elbow. i will see you.}
<A>__{and he's gone. ripley shuts the door, smooths the silk runner on the table where freddie's hand had rucked it. he goes back to the door, opens it and looks over the rail.}
